          (<span class="ref-terms">Adams Papers</span>; endorsed: C. Chavagne 8 June.; docketed by <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Charles Francis Adams (18071886), son of John Quincy Adams and Louisa Catherine Adams ]">CFA</abbr>: 1780.)
        </span>
       </p>

      </div>
      <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA09d274n1-ptr" id="PJA09d274n1">1</a>
       
   <p>No letter from Chavagnes has been found later than that of <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-09-02-0159-0002" class="document">4 May</a>, to which <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> had replied on the <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-09-02-0201" class="document">16th</a> (both above).</p>

